    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/a3c050a1782f6c30152a791a61483278.poster.avif?t=1770033847\" width=1020 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/a3c050a1782f6c30152a791a61483278.webm?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/a3c050a1782f6c30152a791a61483278.mp4?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wanted to become a game developer? Have you ever imagined what would happen if your creativity became reality? Or even worse… when you can’t tell what’s real and what’s not anymore?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is what <strong>Reality Breach</strong> is about.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reality Breach is a <strong>story-driven psychological horror</strong> where the tension doesn’t come from endless jump scares, but from the slow collapse of your mind—and the world around you. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WISHLIST NOW!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/96b66a25370dc514426790ce2b2d3ad5.poster.avif?t=1770033847\" width=1020 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/96b66a25370dc514426790ce2b2d3ad5.webm?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/96b66a25370dc514426790ce2b2d3ad5.mp4?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Physical Threat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re being hunted. You should know your house well… but hiding won’t keep you safe forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/7d1c8e4bebba425d68fa2354de773358.poster.avif?t=1770033847\" width=1020 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/7d1c8e4bebba425d68fa2354de773358.webm?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/7d1c8e4bebba425d68fa2354de773358.mp4?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Psychological Threat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your environment twists against you. What once felt familiar is no longer recognizable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/f7fb88f6d1ab752174526dd59e11977c.poster.avif?t=1770033847\" width=1020 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/f7fb88f6d1ab752174526dd59e11977c.webm?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/f7fb88f6d1ab752174526dd59e11977c.mp4?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Narrative Threat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This story has many ends. Which one will you choose?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/8a53bd7dbe9592dae0e008027806c235.poster.avif?t=1770033847\" width=1020 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/8a53bd7dbe9592dae0e008027806c235.webm?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118910/extras/8a53bd7dbe9592dae0e008027806c235.mp4?t=1770033847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ROADMAP &amp; PERSONAL NOTES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I’m working on Reality Breach <strong>full-time</strong>. The game is nearly complete: content is finished, and I’m now focused on <strong>polishing and bug fixes</strong>.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demo 2.0</strong> is coming soon, giving you the chance to try before you buy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You an track the progress through Trello, linked inside the website section.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The release is very close… this final push is all about making sure it feels right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for following the journey. Your <strong>wishlist and support mean everything</strong>.</p>",
